{
  "stem": "22840.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was the-- it was under the non-German rule, I mean-- not-- not the Slovak rule.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was the uprising.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was the only-- that was really the only place that I can describe to you, between Nove Mesto, except this beautiful recollection of going to the mountain and beautiful, possibly cold weather.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But climbing up, climbing down, it was a big outing for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't realize what was happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I have to credit my mother with it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was no sense of panic that I recall from that time at all.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was just, we have to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was very young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was carried most of the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew nothing about the uprising then at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I became very much interested in-- in what's happening only later in my life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I read very much about the uprising.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's-- it's-- I think, an intriguing story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it reminds me very much of-- of movies like Rashomon, where three people have four different views, so to speak, of what happens.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My view is formed or formulated by couple of approaches, being born in Slovakia and living through that period, being Jewish, and then being, later on, a member of the Israeli armed forces and the Ministry of Defense, and very much interested in-- in tactics and military history.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was always interested in military history, since I became in high school, really, since I became aware of intellectual endeavors.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So from all these points of view, which are very different from my point of view of a Slovak living in Slovakia, the uprising was instigated by Communist forces with cooperation, however, with Western forces.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a tension between them.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
